height_type</span> should be one of       <strong><span>SSH2_TERM_UNIT_CHARS</span></strong> or       <strong><span>SSH2_TERM_UNIT_PIXELS</span></strong>.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ssh2-shell-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns a stream <a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="link">resource</a> on success,  或者在失败时返回 <strong><span>false</span></strong>.  </p> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.ssh2-shell-examples">  <h3 class="title">示例</h3>  <span>   <div class="example" id="">    <p><strong>示例 #1 Requesting an interactive shell</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$connection </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ssh2_connect</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'shell.example.com'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">22</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">ssh2_auth_password</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$connection</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'username'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'password'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$stream </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">ssh2_shell</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$connection</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'vt102'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">null</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">80</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">24</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #9876AA">SSH2_TERM_UNIT_CHARS</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></span></div>    </div>   </div>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ssh2-shell-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ssh2_exec()} - Execute a command on a remote server</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ssh2_tunnel()} - Open a tunnel through a remote server</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link ssh2_fetch_stream()} - Fetch an extended data stream</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
