ink ssh2_sftp_stat()} - Stat a file on a remote filesystem</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link lstat()} - 给出一个文件或符号连接的信息</span></li>    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link stat()} - 给出文件的信息</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
